Been 60 for along time now and and looking forward to some AE grouping for some rapid exp.  It is my understanding that to get efficient mob grouping you will need to get the mobs grouped together in a fairly tight bunch.  What Push back spells are people using for this?<br>
<br>
Think we have:<br>
<br>
Thunder Strike at 29<br>
Thunderclap at 34<br>
Thunderbold at 54<br>
<br>
What do people use to get the mobs close together? Thunderbold seems to be a nice option to push the mobs into a corner.<br>
Comments?<br>
